headline.print_headline: Ryan: Humans Might Not Be Cause of Climate Change
headline.main: Ryan: Humans Might Not Be Cause of Climate Change

lead_paragraph: The planet has faced climate change forever and humans' pollution might not be to blame, Republican U.S. Rep. Paul Ryan said Monday during a debate against his Democratic challenger.
